<node ID="8A76B65D-075F-41EA-9DA8-92BFDA886BB8" TEXT="&#20854;&#20182;" COLOR="#F3F3F3" POSITION="right" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#FF5E69" WIDTH="4" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="20" /><node ID="E496A32B-BBE3-43EE-B3EF-A42060C6CF8D" TEXT="CSS Hack" COLOR="#F3F3F3" POSITION="right" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#FF5E69" WIDTH="3" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="20" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>在一部分浏览器上生效的方法，就称为</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>css hack</span></p><p></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>1. Hack</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>即不合法但是生效的写法</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>2. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>主要区分不同浏览器</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>3. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>缺点：难理解</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>难维护</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>易失效</span></p><p></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>替代方案：</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>1. 特性检测</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>2. 针对性加class</p><p></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>标准属性写前面，</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>hack</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>写后面</span></p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node ID="1E7232D2-EEAB-41BE-BBCD-9FF6BC9B31B3" TEXT="checkbox&#26679;&#24335;" COLOR="#F3F3F3" POSITION="right" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#FF5E69" WIDTH="3" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="20" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
