font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>‘ 语句，可以兼容ie浏览器</span></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>	drop_console: true,</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>// 内嵌定义了但是只用到一次的变量</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>	collapse_vars: true,</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>// 提取出出现多次但是没有定义成变量去引用的静态值</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>	reduce_vars: true</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>    }</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>  }</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>})</p><p></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>项目大再用，按需使用</p></body>
