<node ID="2CD70B34-BEFA-4ECB-BCEB-03F7E2986308" TEXT="&#20107;&#20214;" COLOR="#F3F3F3" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#64AAE1" WIDTH="4" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="20" /><node ID="80B455D2-F758-4857-9899-BCE92B1D8DAC" TEXT="event" COLOR="#F3F3F3" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#64AAE1" WIDTH="3" /><font NAME="Helvetica" SIZE="20" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>1. event.preventDefault() — </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>阻止默认行为</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>2. event.stopPropagation() — </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>阻止冒泡</span></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>3. 不是原生event (SyntheticEvent 组合事件) </p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>4. event.nativeEvent (原生的是MouseEvent)</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>5. event.target 触发节点 (事件触发者)</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>6. event.currentTarget 绑定节点 (事件监听者)</p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<node ID="3BE758A1-266F-4D10-B166-535ED299FAE3" TEXT="target" COLOR="#F3F3F3" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#64AAE1" WIDTH="2" /><font NAME="Helvetica" SIZE="20" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>触发节点</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> (</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>事件触发者</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>)</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>1. event.target === </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>#document</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>2. event.nativeEvent.target === </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>当前节点</span></p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node ID="D8BF9156-F6A9-49F2-A25A-D5431571ACBA" TEXT="currentTarget" COLOR="#F3F3F3" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#64AAE1" WIDTH="2" /><font NAME="Helvetica" SIZE="20" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
