<node ID="4A2A804F-DD87-43BD-AAF3-7A59FBC63937" TEXT="&#20107;&#20214;" COLOR="#F3F3F3" POSITION="left" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#AF4FC8" WIDTH="3" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Regular" SIZE="20" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>1. event</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>参数，自定义参数</span></p><p></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>@click=“increment(2,$event)”</p><p></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>2. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>事件修饰符，按键修饰符</span></p><p></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>只要有ctrl按下就会触发，其他一起按也可以</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>@click.ctrl</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>只有ctrl被按下才会触发</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>@click.ctrl.exact</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>没有任何系统修饰符被按下的时候才触发</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>@click.exact</p><p></p><p></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>3. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>事件被绑定到哪里</span></p><p></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> 1) event </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>是原生的</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> 2</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>) 事件被挂载到当前元素</span></p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
