ingFangSC-Regular"; '>执行</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>render</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>函数，生成</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>vnode</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>，</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>patch</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>(elm, node)</span></p><p></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>更新过程</p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>1. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>修改</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>data</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>，触发</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>setter(</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>此前已经在</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>getter</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>中监听</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>)</span></p><p><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>2. </span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>重新执行</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>render</span><span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>函数，成成newVnode</span></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>3. patch(node, newVode)</p><p></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>异步渲染</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>1. 回顾$nextTick()</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>2. 汇总data的修改，一次性更改视图</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>3. 减少DOM操作次数，提高性能</p><p></p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>总结</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>1. 渲染和响应式的关系</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>2. 渲染和模板编译的关系</p><p style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.000000); font: 16px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>3. 渲染和VDOM的关系 </p></body>
